fulltitle: Ron Carter - 5 questions answered for Discover Double Bass #roncarterbassist
title: Ron Carter - 5 questions answered for Discover Double Bass #roncarterbassist
description:
Here are answers to 5 questions posed to me by my friends at Discover Double Bass.  The questions I am answering are:  

1.  How has your practice routine changed over these last unusual months? 
2.  Who have been your most influential teachers? 
3. What have been some of the most memorable concerts you've played ?
4.  Do you have an exercise routine that helps you? 
5. What kind of gear do you use?
